-- Venezuela ready to present Exxon legal arguments
-- 
-- Wed Feb 13, 2008 7:28pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/14/us-exxon-venezuela-minister-idUSN1339197020080214

 

 CARACAS  (Reuters) - Venezuela will present legal arguments on Thursday in response to temporary court rulings won by Exxon Mobil Corp overseas that freeze up to $12 billion in Venezuelan assets, the oil minister said on Wednesday. 

 (Reporting by  Frank Jack Daniel ; Editing by  Braden Reddall )